$interpreted: Lio: Oh, no! It’s getting light out. I’d better hurry and get this to where sis’ needs it to go!
Lio: Come on! I’m late, I’m late for a very important...thing! I’ve no time to deal with you!
Lio: Wah! It’s already morning, I’d better get running!
Lio: I really hope that Sophie girl hasn’t left the Slums yet!
Hutchinson: Looks like we’ve got no choice but to head back to the Desert Kingdom first.
Ru-yi: I wonder if Clark will be disappointed in us...
Sophie: Rune’s probably worried about us...
Lio: Circus outfits...
Lio: Are you Sophie?
Sophie: Do I know you?
Lio: I’m Lio. I live in the Slums! My sister told me to find you~
Sophie: Sister?
Lio: Yup! My sister is a student at the Rune Academy!
Lio: They want to help you find Headmaster Ceres, but...if they help, Headmaster Balzac will be very angry...
Lio: Wait a sec, I’ll get it!
Sophie: Wah! It can fly! What is that?
Lio: My sister said that when Headmaster Charle left, he took a Rune device called Owl Boy with him.
Lio: And this──is an Owl Egg!
Lio: It can track the Soul Energy flow of Owl Boy. If we use it, we can find Headmaster Charle!
Ru-yi: Wah! Lemme see!!
Hutchinson: Truly worthy of being called Rune Academy. Just as Mr. Clark said. Outstanding.
Hanbei: Hey! A little lower, please!
Lio: And this...this is a user manual that my sister wrote. She said if we don’t understand anything to just take a look at it.
Sophie: And Tica wrote some encouraging words too...thanks so much to all of you!
Ru-yi: Sophie, it’s moving!
Lio: Sophie, you’d best start following it. Good luck finding Headmaster Charle!
Sophie: You got it! Thank you so much. Tell your sister and Tica we said thanks too!
Lio: Great. I completed the request of both Queen Angel and sis~
Charle: Excuse me, have you seen a young boy with silver hair? He’s about this tall, a bit thin...
Male Villager: Naw, ain’t seen nothin’ like that. Best ask around!
Woman Villager: I’m sorry, I haven’t seen him. This is a small village. If someone from outside comes in, we’ll all know!
Charle: I see...thank you.
Charle: *sigh*...Elio, where on earth are you...?
Charle: E? What’s this in Owl Boy’s beak?
Charle: Eh? Is this the Owl egg I left the Academy in case of emergency?
Sophie: Headmaster Charle Ceres!
